  habitat: Myling Habitat
  description: 'The Myling is a spirit of a child murdered by its mother, often returning
    to haunt her as a punishment.  The Myling lingers near the place, where the body
    was hidden - screaming and sobbing in the darkness.  It can take physical form
    in the shape of a giant black bird with a human head. '
